@dervinism = the 2.2b8 is a beta release; not a release yet, hence why the yaml is not updated; we want people to test it, and one feature you asked about was in the latest release, such that you could use it by simply running pip install deeplabcut==2.2b8 inside the open container.

in short, the file does not need edited, but glad it works for you and that it can find your corrupted frames, hence solving the mystery of why those frames are not used by DLC! :)

error codes help: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/22944133/how-can-i-find-out-what-this-ffmpeg-error-code-means
